| 2 Expectations                                                              |
o-----------------------------------------------------------------------------o

Zwischenwelt is a quite stable version. So if things don't work, no panic... fix it :)

o-----------------------------------------------------------------------------o
| 3 What is 'Zwischnwelt'?                                                    |
o-----------------------------------------------------------------------------o

Zwischenwelt is a browser game inspired by Civilisation, Master of Magic, 
and some other games like this. It supports building towns, armies, trading, 
casting spells, and more. The project's language is mostly German.

